            "text": "<p>You can find all of our locations and business hours <a href=\"https:\/\/www.getplenty.com\/pages\/store-locator\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.getplenty.com\/pages\/store-locator\">here<\/a>.<\/p>"
